# gateway-chat.http —— Chat completions（数据平面）。
#
# 路由：/v1/chat/completions（OpenAI 协议；M3 Envelope detector 按路径识别）
#
# 前置链路：admin 已建好对应 model 的 ModelService + Endpoint + active Pricing；
# 拿一个有效 APIKey 明文（admin POST /apikeys 时一次返回）。
#
# 全链路（10 middleware）：
#   M1 TraceContext → M9 Recover → M2 Auth → M3 Envelope → M4 Budget → M5 ModelService
#   → M6 Limit → M8 Moderation → M7 Schedule → 上游 ARK → M10 Tracing
#
# 失败矩阵：
#   - 缺凭证 / hash 不匹配 → 401
#   - model 未在 model_services → 404 "model not found"
#   - model 没 active pricing → 503 "pricing: no active version..."
#   - 没 endpoint 配该 (model, group) → 503 "no endpoint for ..."
#   - body 超 BodyLimit → 413
#   - 上游 5xx → 502
#
# **{{apikey}}** 来自 admin-apikeys.http 或 00-bootstrap.http 里的 client.global.set()；
# 跑这个文件前先在 IDE 里跑一次 admin-apikeys.http 的 Create 拿明文。

### Non-streaming chat（DeepSeek-V3.2）
POST {{gateway_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{apikey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "stream": false,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "用一句话回答你是谁。"}
  ]
}

> {%
client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert(response.status === 200));
client.test("usage filled", () => client.assert(response.body.usage.total_tokens > 0));
client.log("response: " + response.body.choices[0].message.content);
%}

### Streaming chat（SSE；usage 通过 stream_options.include_usage 注入）
POST {{gateway_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{apikey}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "数到 5。"}
  ]
}

### 缺凭证 → 401
POST {{gateway_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "hi"}]
}

> {% client.test("401 unauthorized", () => client.assert(response.status === 401)); %}

### 错的 APIKey → 401（hash mismatch）
POST {{gateway_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer sk-bogus-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "hi"}]
}

> {% client.test("401 invalid creds", () => client.assert(response.status === 401)); %}

### 未注册 model → 404
POST {{gateway_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{apikey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "this-model-does-not-exist",
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "hi"}]
}

> {% client.test("404 model not found", () => client.assert(response.status === 404)); %}

